snippet.title: Mortal Kombat 1 – Invasions Season 7 Trailer
snippet.description:
Decay rises in his wake. Quell the invading Shang Tsung's reign to earn new skins during the
Season of the Soul Eater.

Get the Premium Edition today jump into Invasions Mode now:
https://www.mortalkombat.com/purchase 

It's In Our Blood. Discover a reborn Mortal Kombat Universe created by Fire God Liu Kang. Mortal Kombat 1 ushers in a new era of the iconic franchise with a new fighting system, game modes, and Fatalities!
